stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle
  Idle --> ScanContext: proc_mask != 0
  ScanContext --> QueryDMA: context bit set
  QueryDMA --> ReadStreamBitmap: QUERY_IDLE
  ReadStreamBitmap --> InsertTask: stream ready and not task_valid
  InsertTask --> ScanContext: task inserted
  ReadStreamBitmap --> ScanContext: no new stream
  ScanContext --> Sleep: all contexts scanned
  Sleep --> Idle: rt_thread_delay(10)
